Dark One/Scattershot/Breakdown:



Dark One sidestepped, Stalker going past him.  Raising his weapon, he fired 
off 20 explosive shells at Stalker's back.

---

Scattershot got up, firing 5 armor piercing rounds at Stalker's pelvis from 
behind.

---

Breakdown saw Stalker charging him, and transformed to his artillery mode, 
firing off an explosive shell at the rushing robot's sternum, autoguns coming 
out of the cieling and opening fire on Stalker.
